item.title: CVE-2016-15002|2024-08-06T03:47:34.624Z -- unspecified -- monyog%20ultimate
item.description: A vulnerability, which was classified as critical, was found in MONyog Ultimate 6.63. This affects an unknown part of the component Cookie Handler. The manipulation of the argument HasServerEdit/IsAdmin leads to privilege escalation. It is possible to initiate the attack remotely.
